%% Old version:
% % mode-k folding (inverse of mode-k unfolding -- flatten)
% % tested? - Yes.
% % args:
% %   - A: a matrix
% %   - sz: size of the tensor to fold into
% %   - k: mode of fold
% % return:
% %   - X: a tensor with size sz.
